title: Suzu-tsuki Neko wa Nyao to Naku?
original_name: 鈴付きネコはにゃおと鳴く?
sinopse:
Does the cat with the bell say meow? Found sick on the side of the road, when they first met he was like a stray cat. Nao and Suzu begin their journey with each other in a way, unlike others. Follow this cute, fluffy story as their life and past slowly combines.

(Source: MU)
